-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;">· 工作效率低，无法从思维提升时间管理效率的朋友</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;">· 学习效果差，没有自己的逻辑体系，学习越来越觉得力不从心的朋友。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;">· 突击考试：想要获得先进有效的学习方法，快速吸收资讯、理清思维脉络的朋友</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; border-radius: 5px; padding: 0px 0.75em; background-color: rgb(233, 92, 92); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.9; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">您将获得</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.8; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">快速记忆力+各种能力</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">· 提高时间管理效率：</strong>用1小时完成原来8小时的工作；同1个问题至少想到20种解决方法</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">· 提升阅读速度：</strong>用30分钟看完一本书并记住核心内容；更快地学习新知识与复习整合旧知识。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">· 提升创造与创新能力：</strong>思维过程可视化，让线性思维变“网络化思维”。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">· 提高观察有思考能力：</strong>开发右脑，让1个脑袋变成2个脑袋；能将各种零散的智慧、资源等融会贯通，成为一个系统。</span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section>

01—记忆测试，了解你的大脑

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appYDfMcMtV2307/v_5c1a06adc37cd_3kcfidaE

<section style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.6px; padding: 0px 4px; line-height: 2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3个月，她从零学习通过司法开始；</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">4天，她将整本道德经倒背如流；</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2小时，她把打乱成7200多块碎片的53副油画完美复原；</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">30分钟，她搞定了花234万和巴菲特吃饭的投资人朱晔。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">她说：<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">“我可以在极短时间内记住一个人，但为了让别人记住我，却花了十年”</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">她是卢菲菲，世界记忆大师，菲常记忆创始人，一个一步步向上努力的傻姑娘。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 87%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); margin: -10px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: dotted; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzgtzrSgg2280/image/ueditor/37552500_1523261336.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.6px; padding: 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">《最强大脑》第二季挑战赛中，她挑战辨骨神医“骨哥”史俊恒，在短短两小时内就记住了53幅世界经典油画的7376张碎片！最后挑战成功！</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">最强大脑里有许多记忆大神、比如脑王“王峰”、天才少年“申一帆”、计算天才“饶舜涵”等等...</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">但相比较于他们从小就展现出的超于常人的智力，卢菲菲表示其实自己本身记忆力并不强，如今的她都是通过后天训练而成的。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 87%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); margin: -10px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: dotted; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzgtzrSgg2280/image/ueditor/43287800_1523261336.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.6px; padding: 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">小时候是口吃，</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">她竟然自己治好了</strong></span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">小时候的卢菲菲是个说话不清楚的“大舌头”，“不要跟她玩儿！”面对同学的嘲笑，她常常一个人在一边伤心的掉眼泪。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">父母不忍心看着女儿变得自卑，便带她去做手术，可惜手术失败了。看着辛苦挣钱的父母，她以手术太疼为借口，拒绝了第二次的手术。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">从此便决定自己给自己治病！每天放学后，她就抱着字典，从第一页开始“a,o,e,b-a,ba……”</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">坚持了大半年，奇迹竟然真的出现了，她给自己治好了大舌头的毛病，全家人欣喜不已。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">普通中专毕业，</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">很努力但就是记不住更多的知识</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">学校毕业后，卢菲菲做过酒店前台、扫过厕所，也遭遇过别人的白眼和不理解。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">她也怀疑过人生，但俞敏洪的一次演讲使她再次坚定了对生活的态度。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzgtzrSgg2280/image/ueditor/38215800_1523261336.jpg&#39;); background-position: 51.0827% -9.4556%; background-repeat: repeat; background-size: 107.915%; background-attachment: scroll; padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: justify; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8; padding: 0px 10px; color: rgb(122, 98, 103); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box;">“我们每一个人，都应该像树一样成长，即使我们现在什么都不是，但只要你有树的种子，即使你被踩到泥土中间，你依然能够吸收泥土的养分，自己成长起来。当你长成参天大树后，在很远的地方，人们就能看到你、走近你，你能给人一片绿色。活着是美丽的风景，死了依然是栋梁之才！”</span></p><p style="text-align: right; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 13px; box-sizing: border-box;">———俞敏洪</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.6px; padding: 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">于是她再次扎进了书本的海洋，希望以新的知识改变现状。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">但在看书的时候，发现自己经常会容易睡着，并且很多东西反反复复记不住。她开始想办法提高记忆力，试过核桃、试过大枣，只差脑白金没试过了。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 87%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); margin: -10px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: dotted; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzgtzrSgg2280/image/ueditor/49335300_1523261336.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.6px; padding: 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">3年时间从简陋的出租屋里，</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">走出来的世界记忆大师</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">记忆力是学习一切的基础</strong>，偶然间听说有快速记忆的存在，她开始四处打听。经过几番周转，2008年，她终于开始接触快速记忆，在一个几平米的出租屋里，边工作边努力练习。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;　</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">3年后，在2011年的第二十届世界脑力锦标赛上，她就与来自中、德、日、蒙古等17个国家的130名选手进行比赛，过五关斩六将最后卢菲菲获得了“世界记忆大师”的称号。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">之后还担任了第26届世界脑力锦标赛形象大使。</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 87%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); margin: -10px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: dotted; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzgtzrSgg2280/image/ueditor/58538100_1523261336.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.6px; padding: 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">快速记忆，</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">是我新生命的起点</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">有了一定的名气后，卢菲菲收到全国巡回的邀请，曾经吐字不清的她现在做起了记忆法讲师：给小学生、初中生、高中生、大学生甚至大学教授、企业老总上课。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 87%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); margin: -10px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: dotted; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzgtzrSgg2280/image/ueditor/72926600_1523261336.jpg" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 0.6px; padding: 0px 4px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">她想要帮助更多的人，便开始研发一套适合所有人的开发大脑潜能、提高记忆力的课程，开始创业，也开启了她今后的人生之路。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">经过一段时间的摸爬滚打，终于拿到了徐小平老师的教育融资、获得了全球女性创业工场GirlUp的全力支持。又先后获得精锐教育、丰厚资本等公司的数千万投资。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">当你真正决定做一件事情的时候，全世界都会来帮你！</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">我都可以，</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(233, 92, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">大多数人也都能做到。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">普通人不需要成为什么“世界记忆大师”，但我们<strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">每一个人都需要提高自己的学习和工作效率，乃至实现更好的生活状态。</strong></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">而在某个时刻，你是否被下面这些问题卡住？</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 1px; border-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(112, 109, 109); border-right-color: rgb(112, 109, 109); padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(112, 109, 109); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">·想要英语高分，但连记单词的时间都没有；</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">·想要考取行业资格证，看到一堆资料就头大；</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">·汇报方案时，忘记要说什么而白白错失机会；</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">...</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">·工作忙不过来，却还要为熊孩子的学习成绩担·忧;</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">·年纪越大，学习新事物的效率越来越低...</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 87%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(254, 255, 255); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style=" transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -webkit-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -moz-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); -o-transform: translate3d(-10px, 0px, 0px); margin: -10px 0% 10px; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; box-shadow: rgba(81, 81, 81, 0.54) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0px; padding: 0px; border-style: dotted; border-width: 0px; border-radius: 0px; border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px; width: 100%; overflow: hidden !important; box-sizing: border-box;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appzgtzrSgg2280/image/ueditor/6106200_1523261339.gif" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-