-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;">· 工作效率低，无法从思维提升时间管理效率的朋友</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;">· 学习效果差，没有自己的逻辑体系，学习越来越觉得力不从心的朋友。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;">· 突击考试：想要获得先进有效的学习方法，快速吸收资讯、理清思维脉络的朋友</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 0.5em 0px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; border-radius: 5px; padding: 0px 0.75em; background-color: rgb(233, 92, 92); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.9; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">您将获得</strong></p></section></section></section><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.8; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">快速记忆力+各种能力</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">· 提高时间管理效率：</strong>用1小时完成原来8小时的工作；同1个问题至少想到20种解决方法</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">· 提升阅读速度：</strong>用30分钟看完一本书并记住核心内容；更快地学习新知识与复习整合旧知识。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">· 提升创造与创新能力：</strong>思维过程可视化，让线性思维变“网络化思维”。</span></p><p style="marg